      <title>碧桂园首次未能兑付人民币债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/country-garden-misses-yuan-bond-coupon-payment-for-first-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，碧桂园控股有限公司首次未能支付人民币债券的息票，这加剧了这家中国开发商的困境，该开发商目前正面临寻求海外清算的诉讼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/country-garden-misses-yuan-bond-coupon-payment-for-first-time</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 02:09:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
